Consensus diagnostic criteria for PPH were developed based on the National Institutes of Health and Mayo Clinic series [2,10]. The diagnosis requires a resting or exercise mean pulmonary artery pressures of 25 and 30 mmHg , respectively, with no evidence of secondary causes.
